==English==

=== Etymology ===
From the Latin ''dies'', day, and ''mali'', bad ("bad day").

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ˈdɪzm(ə)l/}}

=== Adjective ===
# disappointingly [[inadequate]]
#:''He received a dismal compensation''
